high_descs: Turn left, walk to the sink.
Pick up the salt shaker in front of the sink.
Turn to the right, walk to the end of the counter.
Put the salt shaker in the bottom cabinet closest to the stove.
Turn around to the other counter.
Pick up the salt shaker by the bread.
Turn back around to the other salt shaker.
Put the salt shaker next to the other salt shaker in the bottom left cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers in the cabinet.

high_descs: Move to the sink to the left of the stove
Pick up a grinder from the counter
Move to the cabinet to the right of the stove
Place the grinder inside the cabinet and close the door
Turn around to the counter behind you
Pick up a grinder from the counter
Move to the cabinet to the right of the stove
Place the grinder inside the cabinet and close the door
anns.task_desc: Put two grinders inside the cabinet to the right of the stove.

high_descs: turn to the left and move forward across the room until facing the sink
pick up the salt shaker that is sitting in front of the sink
turn to the right and move to the cabinet that is to the right of the stove, turn to face the cabinet
open the left side of the cabinet and put the salt shaker into the cabinet and close the door
turn around to face the island where the pepper shaker is to the right of the loaf of bread
pick up the pepper shaker that is to the right of the loaf of bread
turn around to face the cabinet that is to the right of the stove
open the left door of the cabinet, put the pepper shaker into the cabinet to the left of the salt shaker and close the cabinet door
anns.task_desc: put the salt and pepper shakers into the cabinet to the left of the stove
